## Fallback Mechanisms âś…

### Groq API Failure
- âś… Frontend uses default insights if analysis not started
- âś… Backend expected to handle Groq errors gracefully
- âś… Default insights: "No-code builder energy", "Design tools are your playground", "AI-curious, testing new platforms"

### SSE Stream Failure
- âś… `pollForCompletion()` fallback implemented
- âś… Polls every 2s for max 60 attempts (2 minutes)
- âś… Updates store with same data structure

### Missing OAuth Context
- âś… Analyzing screen checks if `analysisId` exists
- âś… Logs warning: "Analysis not started - using fallback insights"
- âś… Still advances through screens normally

